PROJECTS
SmartBrain Face Detection ReactJS Facial Recognition app that is able to detect any faces present in an Image via the Clarifai API. Displays the image with the detected bounding boxes around the faces. Handwritten Digit Classifier WebApp capable of classifying handwritten digits using a trained Convolutional Neural Network in the backend. Model performs at ~ 92% classification success. Utilized Python (Flask) for the Rest API, and Vanilla JS for the UI implementation. SmartBrain Backend API NodeJS/ExpressJS Implementation of the backend for SmartBrain Face Detection. Manages and authenticates user profiles via PostgreSQL databases and KnexJS. StudyBuddies Android App that tracks course progress for students. Allows enablement of notifications for higher priority tasks. Built using Java. Ani's Portfolio My Portfolio website that you're currently looking through! Made using ReactJS.
); } export default Projects;
